These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, cola, mirinda, iced-tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, canadian, mexican, indian, turkish, colombian, polish
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, tennis, skiing, handball, biathlon, rowing, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, helicopter, skateboard, roller, snowmobile, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the indian##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the pakistani is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the turkish##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the scooter and the colombian##2
 9. the turkish is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the mexican##1
14. the colombian is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the polish##1
16. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
17. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the mexican##1
18. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the turkish##1
19. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | lemonade        | iced-tea | cola      | mirinda     | milk      | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indian         | polish   | pakistani | colombian    | turkish | mexican |
| Sport         | skiing | biathlon | lacrosse | tennis | ice-hockey  | rowing  | handball    |
| Transport     | roller  | snowmobile         | motorbike     | bus    | helicopter | skateboard     | scooter     |

