10. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of techno and the person eating apple##2
11. the fan of country is the person eating grapes##1
12. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
13. the fan of folk is between the person eating apple and the fan of jazz##2
14. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
